<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n05173b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n05" href="#n05173b">N05 (VI.B.2)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n05all.htm#n05173b"> 173(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> I verily believe</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">By-the-by, it was in that office Mangan penned his since famous ballad, <i>The Woman of Three Cows</i>, and <mark>I verily believe</mark> the composition did not occupy him half an hour. <small> Alfred Perceval Graves, <a name="ILMS" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#ILMS"><cite title="source">Irish Literary and Musical Studies</cite></a>, (1913) (George Petrie) 224</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
